or downstream ASR. Finally, experiments on both synthetic\nand real noisy datasets demonstrate that Wav2code can solve the speech\ndistortion and improve ASR performance under various noisy conditions,\nresulting in stronger robustness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Apr 2023 04:46:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Apr 2023 03:12:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
