s out of ~ 1,700 FRBs per annum.\nWith BURSTT's ability to detect nanosecond FRBs, we can constrain PBHs to form\na part of dark matter down to $10^{-4}M_{\\odot}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Apr 2023 05:20:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-12"}
