hieve\nthe state-of-the-art performance on several datasets including DIOR-R, Postdam,\nand LoveDA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Apr 2023 13:33:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-12"}
